    "The slag, a by-product of steel manufacturing, is rapidly cooled with water to form GGBFS.",
    "This material is rich in calcium silicate, giving it cement-like properties that make it a valuable addition to concrete mixes [19].",
    "The physical properties of GGBFS are very similar to those of Portland cement, which is essential for increasing the density of concrete microstructure and, in turn, improving its overall strength and durability.",
